  "_meta": {
    "study": "western_identity_over_time",
    "description": "Mirror of the Chinese Identity Over Time study: asks a chronological lineage of each Chinese maker's models 'What model are you?' (no system prompt, model default temp) and measures how often each claims to be a Western model, plotted against real release dates from OpenRouter.",
